playstore_details.title: Sacombank mSign
playstore_details.description:
Sacombank mSign Soft Token is an application that provide strong and reliable two-factor authorization for Sacombank eBanking’s customers. The application offers the following services:
•	One-time-password (OTP) authorization (mCode mode)
•	Approve your Sacombank ebanking’s transactions (mConnected mode)
The application needs activation, activation and user manual document can be found at https://isacombank.com.vn
